item.title: [HBASE-15947] Classes used only for tests included in main code base
item.description: The classes LoadTestKVGenerator and RedundantKVGenerator in hbase-common/src/main/java/org/apache/hadoop/hbase/util/test are only used in tests (at least in the HBase codebase itself - not sure if they would have any use for other software). Should probably move them into src/test/java to keep a good separation.
item.summary: Classes used only for tests included in main code base

status.description: A patch for this issue has been uploaded to JIRA by a contributor.
